text: Death Is Called Engelchen (; ) is a 1963 Czech war movie directed by Ján Kadár and Elmar Klos and starring Jan Kačer, Eva Poláková, Martin Růžek, Blažena Holišová, Otto Lackovič. == Other websites == * Category:1963 war movies Category:Czech movies Category:Movies directed by Ján Kadár Category:Movies directed by Elmar Klos
